{"tid":1849791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《科大學生會就嚴民教授網上言論之聲明》","createTime":"2020-01-29T08:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T02:57:29.000Z","uid":66324,"like":101,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"14214eaa019ca5cd6d5ed0f79363cfc74645c60c","tid":1849791,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:36:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKUSTSU/photos/a.288100644538118/3199979473350206/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKUSTSU%2Fphotos%2Fa.288100644538118%2F3199979473350206%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jqix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=86670c69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKUSTSU/photos/a.288100644538118/3199979473350206/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n《科大學生會就嚴民教授網上言論之聲明》<br />\n<br />\n本會接獲通知，本校數學系教授嚴民於社交媒體表示武漢肺炎被誇大，認為一同前往中国公幹的科大教職員戴着口罩「看著特愚蠢」，又表示香港同事「閉塞貧乏，怪不得什麼都怕」。<br />\n<br />\n本會代表科大為其不負責任言論向廣大市民道歉，嚴教授出生於衛生水平薄弱的中国，相信其言論乃缺乏常識的結果，而非刻意營造肺炎容易散播的環境。<br />\n<br />\n嚴教授又於社交媒體表示口罩「感冒了就戴，不感冒就不戴」，本會在此提醒各位口罩除了防止散播病菌亦用以預防感染病菌，希望嚴教授以實名於網上發表偉論前先動動腦轉轉彎，可能會快快解決了肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n本會呼籲所有學生上嚴教授的課時做足預防措施，防範病菌經唾液傳染。本會亦呼籲嚴教授自行無期隔離，以免傳播愚蠢病。<br />\n<br />\n香港科技大學學生會<br />\n二零二零年一月二十九日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fdet1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/83081500_3199979480016872_798155071358500864_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_ohc=JJmx0pZvKkgAX-PIYoC&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fdet1-1.fna&amp;oh=89c8ded30ebce57f59cca7d83a214a9e&amp;oe=5E9522E3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fdet1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F83081500_3199979480016872_798155071358500864_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_ohc%3DJJmx0pZvKkgAX-PIYoC%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fdet1-1.fna%26oh%3D89c8ded30ebce57f59cca7d83a214a9e%26oe%3D5E9522E3&h=91f546a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"383c50525151ca22c5133a3e9bea0b83cd72455c","tid":1849791,"uid":62290,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />代道歉 靚波"},{"pid":"91b2de3c1bf6c02c766e09f8d96902aaef288fa6","tid":1849791,"uid":177510,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:39:37.000Z","msg":"教授都咁無常識，難怪有一大班盲信中共嘅愚民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0776fb628027463bc2f1505696acb7983882a4e","tid":1849791,"uid":66324,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:39:57.000Z","msg":"嚴民教授涉嫌於科大學生集會對學生郁手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de0fa58c4ccae14c6e9ffe72b366ae883bb2493","tid":1849791,"uid":122275,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:42:49.000Z","msg":"嚴教授出生於衛生水平薄弱的中国，相信其言論乃缺乏常識的結果，而非刻意營造肺炎容易散播的環境。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab369b1ea165fc17c251cd9c6dbd360d5a5debf","tid":1849791,"uid":195048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:43:02.000Z","msg":"笑死"},{"pid":"bda070f17e843c87cdd1e9746d3ea33c7180bfa8","tid":1849791,"uid":116912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"科大學生會好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec918867f06af326672c226654878282d99064cc","tid":1849791,"uid":98860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:49:37.000Z","msg":"靚抽"},{"pid":"6963d87e154f8fb6aafa93b1bb6aa150fa8a2801","tid":1849791,"uid":61395,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:53:16.000Z","msg":"動動腦轉轉彎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09543e080e29bbcc130f222592f1af1965f4c7c3","tid":1849791,"uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"383c50525151ca22c5133a3e9bea0b83cd72455c","tid":1849791,"uid":62